# Copy to apps/web/.env.production (or export at build time). Never commit secrets.
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_* values are INLINED into the client bundle at `next build` time —
# they are NOT runtime config. Rebuild the web app after changing this.
#
# Base URL the browser uses to reach the Nest API. A RELATIVE value keeps the app
# same-origin on BOTH admin.upcarrera.com and admissions.upcarrera.com (nginx
# proxies each origin's /api to the API), which removes the need for any CORS
# config. Use an absolute URL only if the API is served from a different origin.
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=/api
